      "Title": "Gsag.Transactional.Core.Observability.ITransactionObserver",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Gsag.Transactional.Core.Observability.ITransactionObserver.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Receives notifications at each stage of a transaction managed by TransactionProxy.\nRegister an implementation in DI (or pass directly to TransactionProxyFactory.Create)\nto observe transaction events for logging, metrics, or testing.</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "type": "ManagedReference",
      "source_relative_path": "api/Gsag.Transactional.Core.Observability.TransactionInfo.yml",
